Subject: [PATCH] OCCT 8.0.0 compatibility (SMESH / Geom / NETGENPlugin / Netgen)

Rebased from the upstream OCCT 8.0.0 compatibility work by the SMESH
maintainer (oursland/SMESH, branch occt-8.0.0, PR looooo/SMESH#2):
patch/{Geom,SMESH,NETGENPlugin,Netgen}_occt800.patch, with the per-patch
subdirectory roots folded into the paths so the combined patch applies
with -p1 at the source root. The four bundled Netgen src/Netgen/libsrc/occ
files whose upstream hunks assume earlier Netgen patches not present in
this release tarball are handled separately in the next patch.
